## 02_BP战力目标卡片_米白

### 查找正则

```regex
/^\s*-\s*名称:\s*([^|\n]+?)\s*\|\s*BP总值:\s*([+-]?\d+(?:\.\d+)?)\s*\|\s*层级:\s*([^\n]+?)\s*\n\s*操作:\s*([+-]?\d+(?:\.\d+)?)\s*\((.*?)\)\s*\n\s*肉体:\s*([+-]?\d+(?:\.\d+)?)\s*\((.*?)\)\s*\n\s*咒术:\s*([+-]?\d+(?:\.\d+)?)\s*\((.*?)\)\s*\n\s*特性备注:\s*\n((?:\s*-\s*.+(?:\n|$))*)/gm
```

### 替换内容

```html
<div class="bp-target-card"><div class="bp-target-top"><span class="bp-target-name">✦ $1</span><span class="bp-tier">$3</span></div><div class="bp-total"><div class="bp-total-head"><span>BP总值</span><span class="bp-total-value">$2</span></div><div class="bp-total-track"><span class="bp-total-fill" style="--bp-meter:min(100%, calc($2 / 1000 * 100%));"></span></div></div><div class="bp-stat-grid"><div class="bp-stat"><div class="bp-stat-label">操作</div><div class="bp-stat-value">$4</div><div class="bp-stat-note">$5</div></div><div class="bp-stat"><div class="bp-stat-label">肉体</div><div class="bp-stat-value">$6</div><div class="bp-stat-note">$7</div></div><div class="bp-stat"><div class="bp-stat-label">咒术</div><div class="bp-stat-value">$8</div><div class="bp-stat-note">$9</div></div></div><div class="bp-trait-title">特性备注</div><div class="bp-trait-list">$10</div></div>
```

